1. *Jezero* je bilo mirno tokom cijelog dana. (The *lake* was calm throughout the day.)
2. Nalazimo se u blizini *jezera*. (We are near the *lake*.)
3. Vidjeli smo mnogo različitih vrsta riba u *jezeru*. (We saw many different kinds of fish in the *lake*.)
4. *Jezerska* voda je čista i osvježavajuća. (The *lake's* water is clean and refreshing.)
5. Nismo bili sigurni da li bismo mogli voziti kroz *jezero*, ali smo pokušali i uspjeli. (We weren't sure if we could drive through the *lake*, but we tried and succeeded.)
6. Prošli smo pored *jezera* na putu za planinu. (We passed by a *lake* on our way to the mountains.)
7. *Jezerski* vazduh je osvježavajući i pun kiseonika. (The *lake's* air is refreshing and full of oxygen.)
8. Plovimo na *jezeru* svake nedjelje ujutru. (We sail on the *lake* every Sunday morning.)
9. *Jezerski* pejzaž je predivan i smirujući. (The *lake's* landscape is beautiful and calming.)
10. Naša kuća se nalazi pored *jezera*. (Our house is located next to the *lake*.)

Note: In Serbian, the word "jezero" means "lake" in English.